text: Lineynaya () is a rural locality (a railway station) in Lineyninsky Selsoviet, Narimanovsky District, Astrakhan Oblast, Russia. The population was 561 as of 2010. == Geography == It is located 57 km from Astrakhan, 88 km from Narimanov. == References == Category:Rural localities in Narimanovsky District
title: Lineynaya
